  <summary date="2024-01-19T20:32:52Z" status="Introduced in House">South Asian Heart Health Awareness and Research Act of 2023

This bill authorizes the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention to award supplemental grants to states for heart-disease research and awareness among communities disproportionately affected by heart disease, including the South Asian population of the United States.</summary>
